'''舌突蛙属'''(''Liurana'' )是[[无尾目|无尾目]][[亚洲角蛙科|亚洲角蛙科]]的一属动物。原分类在[[浮蛙科|浮蛙科]]<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Yan F |coauthors=Jiang K, Wang K, Jin JQ, Suwannapoom C, Li C, Che J |title=The Australasian frog family Ceratobatrachidae in China,Myanmar and Thailand:discovery of a new Himalayan forest frog clade |journal=Zoological Research |date=2016 |volume=37 |issue=1 |pages=7-14 |doi=10.13918/j.issn.2095-8137.2016.1.7 |pmid=27029870 |url=https://www.cnki.net/kcms/doi/10.13918/j.issn.2095-8137.2016.1.7.html |accessdate=2020-12-03 |archive-date=2021-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418173353/https://www.cnki.net/kcms/doi/10.13918/j.issn.2095-8137.2016.1.7.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在中国，该属中的高山舌突蛙、墨脱舌突蛙、西藏舌突蛙均属于西藏特有物种，全球已知仅分布于西藏东南部的森林中。<ref>{{cite web |title=中国两栖类增加第十三个科：亚洲角蛙科 |url=https://www.sohu.com/a/56813517_119753 |website=搜狐}}</ref>

